(482, 'jobs', 'descriptiobn', 9, 'en', 'Work on the modeling and packaging of dumplings and dumplings, there are also pancakes, pancakes\nThe rate is PLN 13 / h, (up to 26 years old PLN 14 / h), if there is a night shift, the rate is PLN 14 / h\nZmyvak - 13.5 zł / h\nAccommodation is provided in good conditions, withholding PLN 200 from salary\nA sanepid book is required (if you do not have a book, we deduct PLN 100 from the first salary) and a minimum understanding of Polish is required for communication with Kerovniki in production\nMore information by phone\n\nBottom button', '2021-03-25 20:07:08', '2021-03-25 20:07:08'),
